{"tid":2139317,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"嘴裡說疫情，心裡想選情，像極了愛情 劉偉程","createTime":"2020-08-04T08:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T08:01:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b299b9e6f3d8a74f01121f50b9b4b35a5b400bd5","tid":2139317,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"嘴裡說疫情，心裡想選情，像極了愛情<br />\n劉偉程2020/8/4 &mdash; 12:27<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200731-1920_CxOUE_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200731-1920_CxOUE_1200x0.png&h=05c7c591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\nCarrie The Mom 在上周五，公布押後立法會選舉一年的記者會上，有這樣的一句心聲：<br />\n<br />\n「我日日睇住疫情，都無時間理選情。」（Carrie，2020）<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n像極了愛情。<br />\n<br />\n如今，這位仁兄又重施故技了。<br />\n<br />\n香港疫情嚴重，是事實。但醫管局的 500 張社區治療設施病床已就位，若政府願意出力幫忙，再增加這些 reverse triage 的設施，是絕對可行的。而現時的 500 張病床，是由醫管局一手一腳準備的。政府做了甚麼？你唔知，我唔知，單眼佬都唔知。<br />\n<br />\n只知道，政府未來會有一條 line，Carrie 可能會邊冷笑邊說，哎呀醫管局準備 500 張床已經 overload 啦，嗱我呢方面就比較熟，我就話你聽，要佢哋再整呢就唔得㗎啦，好彩有中央大力支持，嚟緊就起兩間臨時醫院！<br />\n<br />\n事實上，綜合各傳媒消息，兩間臨時醫院，連地點、規模都定了。黨就是有效率。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n你說，像不像愛情？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%98%B4%E8%A3%A1%E8%AA%AA%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E5%BF%83%E8%A3%A1%E6%83%B3%E9%81%B8%E6%83%85-%E5%83%8F%E6%A5%B5%E4%BA%86%E6%84%9B%E6%83%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2598%25B4%25E8%25A3%25A1%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%25A3%25A1%25E6%2583%25B3%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2583%2585-%25E5%2583%258F%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E4%25BA%2586%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%2583%2585%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4YdyMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=3278726f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2598%25B4%25E8%25A3%25A1%25E8%